title: Hauptwerk 4.1.1 + Update to 4.2.1
description:
Hauptwerk version 4.1.1 + Update to version 4.2.1 (no chime evaluation 32 and 64-bit)

With the version 4.2.1 (since the version 4.1.1) the wind supply is worldwide available in the advanced edition

Instructions:
-------------

1. Run InstallHauptwerk_v4.1.1.012.exe
2. Follow the installer instructions
3. After installation is complete:

If you want to update to version 4.2.1:
---------------------------------------
4. Unrar hw421003.rar
5. If you have 32-bit OS, copy the content of the hw42100332 to the installation directory
6. If you have 64-bit OS, copy the content of the hw42100364 to the installation directory
7. Run

If you don't want to update to version 4.2.1:
---------------------------------------------
4. If you have 32-bit OS, copy the content of the 32 to the installation directory
5. If you have 64-bit OS, copy the content of the 64 to the installation directory
6. Run
